ttention','1','1249442407SINU'),('Online Status','1','1251084122MTBZ'),('If yes, a confirmation email sent to the author of the ticket after a ticket is successfully saved.','1','1251087468IYER'),('If yes, an email is sent to the author of a ticket to notify that the moderator or support replied to the ticket.<br>','1','1251087468IYES'),('If yes, the assigned moderator of the project where the ticket belongs can receive an email notification when a new a ticket or areply is created.<br>','1','1251087468IYET'),('If yes, the creator of the reply will receive an email which is a copy of reply that he/she created.','1','1251087468IYEU'),('To assigned moderators','1','1251087468IYEV'),('Ticket #','1','1251087469EETU'),('On Creation','1','1251087469EETV'),('On Replies','1','1251087469EETW'),('To assigned moderator','1','1251087469EETX'),('View Tickets','1','1251087473QQLF'),('This listing views all the tickets you submitted.<br><ul><li>Before creating a new ticket, please <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">check if there is already an existing ticket</span> that has addressed your concerns. You can only create a new ticket if your concerns haven\'t been addressed yet.</li><li>To see the replies of the ticket created, just click on the ticket title.</li></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 255);\">More Information:</span> When searching for information in a listing, you can use keywords like the name key or title of the ticket. You can also automatically sort a listing by ticket type or category.','1','1251087477HEHD'),('To create a new canned reply, complete the fields asked:<br><ul><li>Title - the name of the canned reply.</li><li>Category - what category does this canned reply belongs.</li><li>Type - in what type of question does this canned reply belongs to.</li><li>Private - accessible only for the moderators.</li><li>Content - the content or description of the canned reply.</li></ul><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 0, 255);\">NOTE:</span><br><